Phase 7 Tasks 1-2: Scrollback Buffer and Scroll Navigation

Files changed:
  - src/terminal/mod.rs: 7 new scroll methods on Terminal wrapper
  - src/terminal/grid_bridge.rs: viewport-aware extract_grid_cells using display_offset

Implementation:
  - display_offset() → grid.display_offset()
  - history_size() → grid.history_size()
  - scroll_up(lines) → scroll_display(Scroll::Delta(lines))
  - scroll_down(lines) → scroll_display(Scroll::Delta(-lines))
  - scroll_page_up() → scroll_display(Scroll::PageUp)
  - scroll_page_down() → scroll_display(Scroll::PageDown)
  - snap_to_bottom() → scroll_display(Scroll::Bottom)
  - extract_grid_cells: Line(row - offset) for viewport-aware rendering

